<br>
Wait till guild_01 is clearing fear <br>
Zone in ~ bind at n wall SS<br>
find Guild_01 in fear have on of them duel you<br>
leave something on the corpse you wont care if it rots<br>
<br>
park the corpse very close to bg spwn<br>
<br>
goto gfay buy a couple chipped bone rods<br>
gate into fear target self cast bone rod to target corpse and cast bind sight and watch the spwn safely from north SS for how ever long you want<br>
<br>
<br>
~~~<br>
now me personally ate one exp death because i ran in nekkid to plant my corpse but i was reading the above posts here and figured that would be best way ~ no doubt<br>
